on</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"35%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 35.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">10.000\n  đồng/trường hợp</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"7%\" style=\"width: 7.18%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">05</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"56%\" style=\"width: 56.98%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p style=\"margin-top:6.0pt\"><span lang=\"VI\">Thay đổi, cải chính hộ tịch cho\n  người chưa đủ 14 tuổi cư trú ở trong nước</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"35%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 35.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">10.000\n  đồng/trường hợp</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"7%\" style=\"width: 7.18%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">06</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"56%\" style=\"width: 56.98%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p style=\"margin-top:6.0pt\"><span lang=\"VI\">Bổ sung hộ tịch cho công dân Việt\n  Nam cư trú ở trong nước</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"35%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 35.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">10.000\n  đồng/trường hợp</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"7%\" style=\"width: 7.18%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">07</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"56%\" style=\"width: 56.98%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p style=\"margin-top:6.0pt\"><span lang=\"VI\">Cấ</span>p <span lang=\"VI\">giấy xác\n  nh</span>ậ<span lang=\"VI\">n tình trạng hôn nhân</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"35%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 35.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">10.000\n  đồng/trường hợp</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"7%\" style=\"width: 7.18%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background: transparent; padding: 0in;\">\n  <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"VI\">08</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"56%\" style=\"width: 56.98%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windo